# 7. 熱気と迷い

Ichika: Hehe. I never expected I'd get to go to a Miku concert with you, Honami.
Honami: I'm sorry for asking you so suddenly.  You even helped me find a ticket on resale too...
Ichika: Don't mention it! I was happy to!
Ichika: But I am still a bit surprised. Is there a song that you want to hear?
Honami: Not exactly... I just want to know more.
Ichika: Know more?
Honami: Yes. You're always telling us all about how great Miku is, but I really don't know much about VIRTUAL SINGERs in general...
Honami: That's why I want to know more about their fans, and how they think and what they feel from their music.
Ichika: I see... Then, today's show should be perfect.
Ichika: I mean, it's going to be full of people who really love Miku!
Honami: Right...! I'm very much looking forward to it.
Honami: What an incredible atmosphere...
Ichika: Honami?
Honami: Oh, I'm sorry... I was a little overwhelmed, is all.
Honami: I've seen some streams of Miku concerts, so I knew that a lot of people would be in attendance, but even so...
Ichika: Yeah, I know how you feel.
Ichika: It's easy to see online that she's popular, but it's hard not to be a bit stunned when you see all these people here in real life.
Honami: Exactly. I can even see people here who look like they came from overseas.
Ichika: It really makes me happy knowing Miku has fans all around the world.
Honami: Yes, I can understand that.
Honami: Oh, the lights...
Ichika: I think it's starting.
Ichika: There's Miku...!
Miku: Thank you for coming today, everyone!
Miku: I promise to sing with everything I have, so I hope you all really enjoy yourselves today!
Honami: (...! What a roar...)
Miku: ♪——————————
Audience: Yes...! I can't believe she's singing this song first!
Audience: Miku! Look this way for us!
Honami: (It feels so different from watching it on a screen...)
Honami: (I can feel the fans' passion and excitement so clearly...!)
Honami: (Not only that...)
Miku: I can hear you all loud and clear! For this next song, let's sing the chorus together.
Miku: ♪—————— ♪——————...
Audience: I love this song so much...!
Audience: Me too! Every time I listen to it, it reminds me that I'm not alone...
Honami: (These people don't just love Miku...)
Honami: (They genuinely love the music they hear through Miku too.)
Honami: (If Leo/need... If Ichika and Saki wrote a song for them...)
Honami: (I think they would understand and accept the feelings in their music.)
Honami: (I want to see that...)
Honami: (The moment Leo/need's music touches their hearts.)
Miku: ♪——————! ♪——————!
Ichika: Miku really is the best...!
Honami: (Ichika's having so much fun.)
Honami: (Of course she is... Miku's always meant so much to her.)
Ichika: In that case... I'm leaning towards the Fan Festival.
Honami: ...
Honami: (Writing a song for the Fan Festival...)
Honami: (That would make Ichika so happy.)
Ichika: *Sigh* That was so much fun...
Honami: Yes, it was. My heart's still racing.
Ichika: Really? I'm glad you enjoyed yourself too.
Honami: I did! And...it really was amazing.
Ichika: What was?
Honami: I could feel how much everyone in attendance loves Miku...
Honami: Or rather, I think I understand now just how passionate they are about VIRTUAL SINGERs.
Ichika: *Nod* I feel the same way every time I go to one of these.
Honami: (But...)
Ichika: Are you thinking about the new song?
Honami: Oh...
Honami: Yes, that's right.
Honami: I've been doing as much research as I can to figure out which event to choose, but...
Ichika: I see...
Ichika: Hey, Honami?
Honami: Hm?
Ichika: I'm glad that you're thinking so much about us as the leader of our band.
Ichika: Thanks to you, we're able to focus on the prep work for our show.
Ichika: But it also doesn't really feel right for you to worry about this all by yourself.
Ichika: So... Please don't try to shoulder it all on your own, okay?
Honami: Okay... Thank you, Ichika.
